{"TopicId":170278,"ForumId":29,"TopicTitle":"What event is fired when a ship (.craft file) is opened in the editor?","CreatedByName":"UnityNewb","CreatedById":184548,"CreatedDateTime":"2018-01-30T18:32:48Z","PageNum":1,"Articles":[{"CreatedByName":"UnityNewb","CreatedById":184548,"CreatedDateTime":"2018-01-30T18:32:48Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nHi,\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nI\u0027m writing an \u0022auto-autostrut\u0022 mod, and it works well enough except when a new ship is loaded (if the user clicks \u0022Open\u0022 and then selects a craft).\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nI can\u0027t figure out which event is fired once the craft file has been loaded in the editor.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nI have looked around in the API documentation\u00A0but unfortunately in the\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cpre class=\u0022ipsCode prettyprint lang-html prettyprinted\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cspan class=\u0022pln\u0022\u003EGameEvents\u003C/span\u003E\u003C/pre\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u00A0and\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cpre class=\u0022ipsCode prettyprint lang-html prettyprinted\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cspan class=\u0022pln\u0022\u003EEditorLogic\u003C/span\u003E\u003C/pre\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u00A0classes I can\u0027t find anything.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nAny help is much appreciated.\n\u003C/p\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Benjamin Kerman","CreatedById":172792,"CreatedDateTime":"2018-01-31T01:04:12Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nBoth this\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\n\u003Ca href=\u0022https://kerbalspaceprogram.com/api/class_game_events.html#a1732469524d311ab23fd28be88cffa10\u0022 rel=\u0022\u0022\u003Ehttps://kerbalspaceprogram.com/api/class_game_events.html#a1732469524d311ab23fd28be88cffa10\u003C/a\u003E\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nand this may be of interest to you.\u00A0\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Ciframe allowfullscreen=\u0022\u0022 data-controller=\u0022core.front.core.autosizeiframe\u0022 data-embedcontent=\u0022\u0022 data-embedid=\u0022embed8061734494\u0022 scrolling=\u0022no\u0022 src=\u0022https://forum.kerbalspaceprogram.com/index.php?/topic/153112-ksp-122-gameevents-extension/\u0026amp;do=embed\u0022 style=\u0022height:211px;max-width:502px;\u0022\u003E\u003C/iframe\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nEdit: also\u00A0\u003Ca href=\u0022https://kerbalspaceprogram.com/api/class_editor_logic.html#a31c3318fa0d72010668bb605d59b58ea\u0022 rel=\u0022\u0022\u003Ehttps://kerbalspaceprogram.com/api/class_editor_logic.html#a31c3318fa0d72010668bb605d59b58ea\u003C/a\u003E\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cspan class=\u0022ipsType_reset ipsType_medium ipsType_light\u0022 data-excludequote=\u0022\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cstrong\u003EEdited \u003Ctime datetime=\u00222018-01-31T01:05:27Z\u0022 title=\u002201/31/2018 01:05  AM\u0022 data-short=\u00226 yr\u0022\u003EJanuary 31, 2018\u003C/time\u003E by Benjamin Kerman\u003C/strong\u003E\n\u003Cbr\u003EAdded new thing\n\u003C/span\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"UnityNewb","CreatedById":184548,"CreatedDateTime":"2018-01-31T01:23:35Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nOoh thank you!\u00A0onEditorLoad is the correct event. I remember seeing it when looking at the API but I thought\u00A0it was triggered when the editor scene was done loading...\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nAlso thanks for the link that shows the GameEvents extension possibilities, that is pretty useful and cool to know about\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cp\u003E\nedit: thanks again lol I spent a few hours on this the other day\n\u003C/p\u003E\n\u003Cspan class=\u0022ipsType_reset ipsType_medium ipsType_light\u0022 data-excludequote=\u0022\u0022\u003E\n\u003Cstrong\u003EEdited \u003Ctime datetime=\u00222018-01-31T02:11:35Z\u0022 title=\u002201/31/2018 02:11  AM\u0022 data-short=\u00226 yr\u0022\u003EJanuary 31, 2018\u003C/time\u003E by UnityNewb\u003C/strong\u003E\n\u003C/span\u003E\n"},{"CreatedByName":"Benjamin Kerman","CreatedById":172792,"CreatedDateTime":"2018-01-31T04:59:12Z","Content":"\n\u003Cp\u003E\nHappy to help \u003Ca contenteditable=\u0022false\